{{> header}}

{{> toplogo}}

{{#if recipient.collective.name}}
<p>{{recipient.collective.name}},</p>
{{else}}
<p>Hi,</p>
{{/if}}

<p>Just a quick note to let you know that {{remoteUser.collective.name}} (cced) added you as a {{role}} to <a href="https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}">{{collective.name}} {{collective.type}}</a> on Open Collective.</p>

{{#if isAdmin }}
<p>As a core contributor you have ADMIN permissions. That means that you can approve and reject expenses that have been submitted to your collective. You can do so with one click from the email notification or via the interface on https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}/expenses.</p>
{{else}}
<p>As a contributor you have MEMBER permissions. That means that you can submit expenses (https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}/expenses/new) and create new events (https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}/events/new).</p>
{{/if}}

